      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">227.7200</ph> Scope of subpart.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody " outputclass="List1">
         <p class="- topic/p " outputclass="List1">
            <ph rev="Revised March 22, 2023">(a)</ph>This subpart—</p>
         <p outputclass="List2" class="- topic/p ">(<ph rev="Revised March 22, 2023">1</ph>) Prescribes policies and procedures for the acquisition of computer software and computer software documentation, and the rights to use, modify, reproduce, release, perform, display, or disclose such software or documentation. It implements<ph rev="Revised March 22, 2023"> </ph>the following laws and Executive <ph rev="Revised March 22, 2023">o</ph>rder:</p>
         <p outputclass="List3">(<ph rev="Revised March 22, 2023">i</ph>) 10 U.S.C. 3013. </p>
         <p outputclass="List3">(<ph rev="Revised March 22, 2023">ii</ph>) 10 U.S.C. 3208(d). </p>
         <p outputclass="List3">(<ph rev="Revised March 22, 2023">iii</ph>) 10 U.S.C. 3771-3775. </p>
         <p outputclass="List3">(<ph rev="Revised March 22, 2023">iv</ph>) 10 U.S.C. 3781-3786.</p>
         <p outputclass="List3" rev="Revised March 22, 2023">(v) 10 U.S.C. 4576.</p>
         <p outputclass="List3" class="- topic/p ">(<ph rev="Revised March 22, 2023">vi</ph>) Executive Order 12591 (subsection 1(b)(<ph rev="Revised March 22, 2023">7</ph>)).</p>
         <p outputclass="List2" class="- topic/p ">(<ph rev="Revised March 22, 2023">2</ph>) Does not apply to— </p>
         <p outputclass="List3" class="- topic/p ">(<ph rev="Revised March 22, 2023">i</ph>) Computer software or computer software documentation acquired under GSA schedule contracts; or</p>
         <p outputclass="List3" class="- topic/p ">(<ph rev="Revised March 22, 2023">ii</ph>) Releases of computer software or computer software documentation to litigation support contractors (see subpart <xref href="SUBPART_204.74.dita#DFARS_SUBPART_204.74"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly">204.74</xref>).</p>
         <p outputclass="List1" rev="Revised March 22, 2023"> (b) See <xref href="PGI_227.7200.dita#DFARS_PGI_227.7200"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly">227.7200</xref> (b) for guidance and information in DoD issuances.</p>
